Market Notification: After the Day-Ahead Market closed, PDCI (S-N) TTC has
been changed from 1407 MW to 1380 MW and PDCI (N-S) TTC has been changed
from 1816 MW to 1720 MW starting HE23 for operating day 2/6/02. This is due
to a Celilo Valve Group #3 forced out of service. No ETR. The first
applicable hour to submit adjusted schedules in the Hour-Ahead Market is HE4
for operating day 2/7/02. Inquiries please call (916) 351-4409.  Please
address real-time operational inquiries to the Real-Time scheduling desk at
(916) 351-2493, or (916) 351-4409.

The system conditions described in this communication are dynamic and
subject to change.  While the ISO has attempted to reflect the most current,
accurate information available in preparing this notice, system conditions
may change suddenly with little or no notice.
